%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20found%20the%20following%20items%20for%20free%20in%20brand%20new%2C%20like%20new%2C%20or%20gently%20used%20condition%3A%20a%20convertible%20crib%20(worth%20about%20%24200)%2C%20a%20high%20chair%20(worth%20about%20%2470)%2C%20a%20booster%20seat%20(worth%20about%20%2460)%2C%20a%20baby%20blender%20set%20(worth%20about%20%2450)%2C%20a%20sit-me-up%20chair%20(worth%20about%20%2440)%2C%20an%20umbrella%20stroller%20(worth%20about%20%2440)%2C%20an%20infant%20bath%20tub%20(worth%20about%20%2440)%2C%20a%20dozen%20sippy%20cups%20(worth%20about%20%2430)%2C%20a%20bottle%20set%20(worth%20about%20%2430)%2C%20a%20sit-to-stand%20walker%20(worth%20about%20%2425)%2C%20microwavable%20sterilizing%20bags%20(worth%20about%20%2415)%20breast%20milk%20freezer%20bags%20(worth%20about%20%2410)%2C%20a%20bottle%20drying%20rack%20(worth%20about%20%2410)%2C%20and%20tons%20of%20burp%20cloths%2C%20swaddles%2C%20blankets%2C%20and%20bags%20full%20of%20clothes%20from%20size%20newborn%20up%20to%2018%20months%20(worth%20hundreds%20of%20dollars).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d73f384e-3b0f-4a9e-968b-786015c4d969%5C%22%3EFree%20kids'%20sports%20gear%20has%20saved%20us%20hundreds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20gotten%20our%20older%20daughter%20three%20different%20bikes%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-marketplace-key-to-meta-getting-gen-z-younger-users-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFacebook%20Marketplace%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20our%20neighbors'%20curb%20giveaways%20that%20have%20saved%20us%20about%20%24300%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20other%20than%20having%20to%20invest%20%2420%20to%20get%20the%20brakes%20repaired%20on%20one%20of%20them%2C%20they've%20otherwise%20been%20in%20great%20working%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223549%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20young%20girl%20does%20a%20flip%20on%20a%20gymnastics%20bar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6877be8cf748d8c055f5b45d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20oldest%20daughter%20and%20her%20friends%20spend%20hours%20practicing%20their%20gymnastics%20moves%20on%20this%20second-hand%20set.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mary%20Kearl%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20gotten%20a%20free%20skateboard%20and%2C%20after%20seeing%20our%20activity%20in%20a%20local%20giveaway%20group%2C%20one%20of%20our%20neighbors%20offered%20us%20a%20gymnastics%20bar%2C%20beam%2C%20and%20mat%20set%20(worth%20about%20%24250)%20directly%20instead%20of%20posting%20it%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20some%20misses%2C%20including%20a%2030-year-old%20ping%20pong%20table%20that%20took%20three%20adults%20to%20move%20and%20only%20ended%20up%20lasting%20one%20season%20before%20falling%20apart.%20But%20over%20the%20years%20we've%20scored%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20finds%20and%20we%20plan%20to%20keep%20getting%20items%20for%20our%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20and%20giving%20away%20things%20we%20no%20longer%20need%20%E2%80%94%20for%20free%20when%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-shares-tips-for-getting-secondhand-kid-items-for-free-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753100291000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6877bc1d3d5881a51c1d6bab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-shares-tips-for-getting-secondhand-kid-items-for-free-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Raising%20kids%20is%20expensive%2C%20so%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20try%20to%20get%20as%20many%20second%20hand%20items%20as%20we%20can.%20Here's%20how%20we've%20scored%20clothes%2C%20a%20swing%20set%2C%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mary%20Kearl)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-shares-tips-for-getting-secondhand-kid-items-