e%20the%20benchmark%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20jumped%2011%25.%20The%20company%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20stock's%20struggles%2C%20the%20five%20Berkshire%20gurus%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20are%20mostly%20positive%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-succession-plan-greg-abel-shareholders-react-challenges-ahead-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAbel's%20prospects%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208b05226-0d56-4e9b-b8f2-1130b1442d25%5C%22%3EA%20change%20in%20management%20style%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221135%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Greg%20Abel%20standing%20and%20speaking%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20Energy%20sign.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F54f3b04069bedd8a35797d88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22635%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreg%20Abel%20is%20the%20head%20of%20Berkshire's%20non-insurance%20operations.%3Cp%3EBerkshire%20Hathaway%20Energy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELarry%20Cunningham%2C%20the%20author%20of%20several%20books%20about%20Buffett%20and%20the%20director%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Delaware's%20Weinberg%20Center%2C%20predicted%20a%20change%20in%20management%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGreg%20Abel%20is%20an%20operator%20at%20heart%20%E2%80%94%20he'll%20engage%20more%20directly%20with%20underperforming%20subsidiaries%2C%20unlike%20Buffett%2C%20who%20was%20famously%20hands-off%2C%26quot%3B%20Cunningham%20said.%20%26quot%3BBerkshire%20will%20become%20known%20for%20'intelligent%20autonomy.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20Check%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Check%20Capital%20Management%20and%20a%20longtime%20Berkshire%20shareholder%2C%20anticipated%20a%20similar%20shift.%20Berkshire%20%26quot%3Bmay%20actually%20be%20managed%20better%26quot%3B%20by%20Abel%20as%20he's%20%26quot%3Bmore%20of%20a%20hands-on%20people%20manager%20than%20Buffett%2C%20whose%20number%20one%20interest%20was%20capital%20allocation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20also%20nodded%20to%20Charlie%20Munger's%202014%20shareholder%20letter%2C%20in%20which%20Buffett's%20late%20business%20partner%20hailed%20Abel%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffetts-words-of-praise-for-ajit-jain-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAjit%20Jain%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20boss%20of%20Berkshire's%20insurance%20operations%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bworld-leading%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20some%20important%20ways%2C%20each%20is%20a%20better%20business%20executive%20than%20Buffett.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225795%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Warren%20Buffett%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1ed8ab8b41a9673fa75bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBerkshire's%20stock%20has%20fallen%20since%20Warren%20Buffett%20announced%20he%20was%20stepping%20down.%3Cp%3ENati%20Harnik%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Smead%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Smead%20Capital%20Management%20and%20a%20Berkshire%20investor%20for%20more%20than%2030%20years%2C%20championed%20Abel%20as%20a%20skilled%20business%20acquirer.%20He%20said%20Berkshire's%20%26quot%3Bstrength%20will%20probably%20be%20in%20buying%20whole%20companies%20because%20that%20will%20be%20Greg%20Abel's%20strength.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerkshire%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-succession-planning-greg-abel-stock-billionaires-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eacquired%20many%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20Buffett's%20tenure%2C%20including%20National%20Indemnity%20in%201967%2C%20See's%20Candies%20in%201972%2C%20Nebraska%20Furniture%20Mart%20in%201983%2C%20Geico%20in%201996%2C%20BNSF%20Railway%20in%202010%2C%20Precision%20Castparts%20in%202016%2C%20Alleghany%20in%202022%2C%20and%20Pilot%20Travel%20Centers%20over%20a%20series%20of%20transactions%20in%202017%2C%202023%2C%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerkshire%20generated%20%24371%20billion%20in%20revenue%20and%20%2447%20billion%20in%20operating%20profits%20last%20year.%20It's%20become%20so%20big%20that%20there%20are%20very%20few%20companies%20it%20could%20acquire%20that%20would%20materially%20boost%20its%20bottom%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett's%20biggest%20acquisition%20to%20date%20was%20buying%20Precision%20for%20more%20than%20%2432%20billion%20nearly%20a%20decade%20ago.%20He%20said%20at%20this%20year's%20meeting%20that%20he%20would%20happily%20shell%20out%20%24100%20billion%20for%20the%20right%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbel%20is%20set%20to%20receive%20support%20from%20Jain%20along%20with%20Berkshire's%20investment%20managers%2C%20Todd%20Combs%20and%20Ted%20Weschler%2C%20who%20each%20manage%20chunks%20of%20Berkshire's%20roughly%20%24300%20billion%20stock%20portfolio.%20The%20company's%20biggest%20holdings%20include%20American%20Express%2C%20Apple%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20Coca-Cola%2C%20and%20Chevron.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmead%20said%20Berkshire's%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20mistake%26quot%3B%20was%20not%20publicly%20touting%20Combs%20and%20Weschler's%20track%20records%20as%20investors%20more%20often%2C%20as%20this%20could%20have%20reassured%20shareholders%20about%20the%20post-Buffett%20era%20and%20tempered%20the%20recent%20stock%20decline%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Longo%20%E2%80%94%20a%20finance%20professor%2C%20investment%20chief%2C%20and%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BBuffett's%20Tips%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20echoed%20Smead%20in%20predicting%20Abel%20would%20be%20more%20active%20in%20striking%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELongo%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bwould%20not%20be%20shocked%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20Berkshire%20begin%20paying%20a%20small%20dividend%20given%20its%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-memes-stock-market-crash-cash-pile-apple-quotes-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenormous%20cash%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20strong%20free%20cash%20flow.%26quot%3B%20That%20could%20help%20%26quot%3Battract%20a%20new%20class%20of%20investors%26quot%3B%20and%20fuel%20a%20stock%20rally%2C%20Longo%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrett%20Gardner%2C%20an%20analyst%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BBuffett's%20Early%20Investments%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20that%20Buffett%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-ceo-resignation-investing-succession-greg-abel-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplans%20to%20remain%20chairman%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20can%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20if%20needed.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20praised%20the%20company's%20core%20assets%20and%20board%2C%20and%20described%20Abel%20as%20%26quot%3Bimmensely%20talented.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Buffett%20was%20%26quot%3Birreplaceable%26quot%3B%20but%20added%20that%2C%20with%20Abel%2C%20%26quot%3BBerkshire%20is%20still%20in%20superb%20hands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-greg-abel-berkshire-succession-stock-management-acquisitions-dividend-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753099362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687e054085e81483682e58d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-greg-abel-berkshire-succession-stock-management-acquisitions-dividend-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20of%20Warren%20Buffett's%20closest%20followers%20told%20BI%20they%20expect%20Greg%20Abel%20to%20be%20more%20hands-on%2C%20focus%20on%20deals%2C%20and%20perhaps%20even%20introduce%20a%20dividend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40businessinsider.com%20(Theron%20Moh