ple%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20parents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20smiling%20across%20an%20aisle%20in%20a%20plane%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20from%20LAX.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68781cbef748d8c055f5c17e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20flew%20from%20LAX%20to%20Las%20Vegas.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6fbb747-52c1-4953-b1f4-148452ab05ee%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20let%20ourselves%20luxuriate%2C%20and%20food%20was%20a%20highlight%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20decided%20to%20spend%20two%20of%20those%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flas-vegas-mistakes-first-visit-girls-trip-travel-tips-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enights%20in%20nearby%20Las%20Vegas%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20staying%20at%20Crockfords%2C%20the%20most%20luxurious%20of%20the%20three%20hotels%20within%20the%20Resorts%20World%20complex.%20It%20felt%20elevated%20from%20the%20moment%20we%20stepped%20into%20the%20serene%2C%20artfully%20designed%20lobby.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20nights%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20dressing%20up%20for%20dinner.%20We%20ate%20at%20Nobu%20in%20Caesars%20first%20night%2C%20and%20the%20second%20night%2C%20we%20indulged%20in%20dinner%20at%20Stubborn%20Seed%2C%20from%20Michelin-starred%20chef%20Jeremy%20Ford%2C%20before%20heading%20to%20see%20Nas%20perform%20with%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Philharmonic%20at%20the%20Encore%20Theater%20%E2%80%94%20a%20genre-defying%20experience%20that%20felt%20both%20exhilarating%20and%20intimate.%20We%20were%20fully%20present.%20And%20honestly%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20revelation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20brunch%2C%20we%20snagged%20a%20table%20at%20Pinky's%20by%20Lisa%20Vanderpump%20inside%20the%20Flamingo%2C%20a%20delightfully%20over-the-top%20spot%20that%20leans%20into%20glamour%3B%20yes%2C%20I%20had%20an%20espresso%20martini%20before%20noon.%20Afterward%2C%20we%20walked%20over%20to%20the%20new%20Go%20Pool%2C%20Flamingo's%20dayclub-style%20adults-only%20pool%20party%2C%20and%20set%20up%20shop%20in%20a%20shaded%20cabana.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20the%20DJ%20shouted%20out%20all%20the%20parents%20who'd%20left%20their%20kids%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20exchanged%20a%20knowing%20smile.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20by%20the%20pool%20in%20the%20sun%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20wearing%20sunglasses%20and%20holding%20a%20drink.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68781cebf748d8c055f5c186%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20enjoyed%20lounging%20by%20the%20pool%20and%20reconnecting%20with%20each%20other.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa34c6f8-d4e2-4659-be54-43814f0ebb0f%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20recharged%20individually%20and%20as%20a%20couple%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20spent%20a%20couple's%20afternoon%20at%20the%20expansive%20Awana%20Spa%2C%20where%20sprawling%20co-ed%20pools%20and%20lounges%20provided%20a%20soothing%20backdrop%20for%20tackling%20topics%20big%20and%20small.%20While%20we%20were%20there%2C%20we%20even%20had%20a%20breakthrough%20about%20a%20long-simmering%20plan%20to%20expand%20our%20house%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20of%20epiphany%20that%20can%20only%20happen%20when%20you%20can%20hear%20yourself%20think%20for%20more%20than%20five%20minutes%20in%20a%20stretch.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20long%2C%20uninterrupted%20conversations.%20We%20gambled%20(well%2C%20I%20did%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20say%20it's%20my%20guilty%20pleasure%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20no%20shame)%2C%20ate%20fabulous%20meals%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20the%20kind%20of%20indulgent%2C%20unstructured%20hours%20that%20feel%20impossible%20when%20you're%20deep%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-dads-paradox-coparenting-breadwinner-office-home-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edaily%20grind%20of%20parenting%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20while%2C%20we%20were%20getting%20photo%20updates%20from%20the%20camp%20app.%20I%20scanned%20each%20image%20for%20signs%20of%20either%20joy%20or%20homesickness%2C%20and%20was%20relieved%20to%20see%20the%20kids%20grinning%2C%20making%20new%20friends%2C%20and%20stringing%20up%20freshly%20dipped%20tie-dye%2C%20just%20as%20I%20had%20done.%20They%20were%20more%20than%20OK%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20thriving.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20at%20dinner%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20in%20a%20red%20booth.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68781d1ef748d8c055f5c18d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20enjoyed%20long%20conversations%20over%20good%20food.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20time%20we%20returned%2C%20we%20felt%20recharged%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20individually%2C%20but%20as%20a%20couple.%20That%20reconnection%20was%20badly%20needed%2C%20and%20we%20knew%20it.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20we%20picked%20up%20the%20kids%20from%20camp%20and%20saw%20they'd%20grown%20in%20just%20five%20days%20%E2%80%94%20a%20little%20taller%20somehow%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20more%20confident.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20grown-folks-only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flas-vegas-mistakes-first-visit-girls-trip-travel-tips-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVe