orward%20into%20the%20future%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20plans%20to%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bdemocratic%26quot%3B%20approach%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-be-successful-at-the-big-four-partners-advice-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleadership%20at%20the%20Big%20Four%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20all%20work%20together%20to%20ensure%20that%20we're%20bringing%20the%20best%20that%20we%20can%20for%20our%20clients%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdamski%20joins%20the%20Big%20Four%20firm%20as%20cyber%20threats%20are%20growing%20in%20scale%20and%20severity%2C%20particularly%20for%20US%20businesses.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20US%20data%20breach%20was%20%249.48%20million%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20world%20and%20nearly%20double%20the%20global%20average%20of%20%244.9%20million%2C%20according%20to%20IBM's%202024%20%26quot%3BCost%20of%20a%20Data%20Breach%26quot%3B%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdamski%20told%20BI%20that%20adversaries%20adapt%20their%20techniques%20and%20procedures%20every%20time%20a%20cyber%20defender%20implements%20a%20different%20solution%2C%20so%20businesses%20should%20constantly%20adapt%20their%20cybersecurity%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20about%20understanding%20the%20landscape%2C%20understanding%20where%20you're%20holding%20that%20risk%2C%20putting%20mitigations%20in%20place%2C%20and%20ensuring%20that%20your%20crown%20jewels%20are%20not%20the%20things%20that%20you're%20putting%20at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20forward%20to%20the%20next%205%20to%2010%20years%2C%20the%20cybersecurity%20expert%20said%20two%20factors%20are%20on%20her%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20AI%20means%20that%20companies%20are%20going%20to%20have%20to%20move%20a%20lot%20faster%20on%20evolving%20cyber%20defense%2C%20Adamski%20said.%20Second%2C%20and%20more%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bfuture%20thought%20for%20companies%2C%26q