3EMoleskine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%2018%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-in-nyc-moving-from-midwest-differences-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20summer%20to%20work%20for%20Ralph%20Lauren.%20It%20was%20my%20first%20real%20taste%20of%20independence.%20I%20was%20staying%20with%20friends%20of%20friends%20and%20had%20no%20responsibility%20to%20anyone%20else%2C%20other%20than%20calling%20my%20parents%20once%20a%20week%20to%20let%20them%20know%20I%20was%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20work%2C%20I%20was%20exposed%20to%20so%20much%20beauty.%20There%20was%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20flagship%20store%2C%20a%20mansion%20at%2072nd%20and%20Madison%2C%20and%20the%20grandeur%20of%20celebrities%20coming%20through.%20I%20got%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-of-princess-diana-as-an-amazing-mother-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emeet%20Princess%20Diana%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20actor%20Tom%20Selleck.%20It%20was%20enlightening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ward%20Simmons%20posing%20with%20Ralph%20Lauren%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68625e0ef748d8c055f49e78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22968%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWard%20Simmons%20moved%20to%20NYC%20to%20work%20at%20Ralph%20Lauren.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ward%20Simmons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwriting-things-out-helps-me-manage-my-anxiety-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20wrote%20down%20every%20detail%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20summer%20in%20my%20notebook%2C%20in%20cursive%20penmanship%20that%20looked%20gorgeous%20on%20the%20page.%20Writing%20in%20cursive%20felt%20romantic%20and%20eloquent.%20Now%20that%20I'm%2057%2C%20looking%20back%20on%20those%20notebooks%20and%20seeing%20the%20city%20through%20my%20fresh%2018-year-old%20eyes%20makes%20me%20stop%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3Bwoah.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc64543b-3066-4654-8469-18138f453df7%5C%22%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20north%20and%20south%2C%20with%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20two%20worlds%2C%20split%20between%20the%20north%20and%20the%20south.%20My%20family%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-moved-to-new-york-from-kentucky-surprising-things-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20farm%20in%20Kentucky%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20also%20a%20home%20in%20New%20York.%20During%20my%20formative%20years%2C%20I%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20at%20boarding%20school%20in%20Memphis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds.%20In%20my%20family%2C%20manners%20and%20respect%20meant%20everything%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20I%20was.%20I%20had%20the%20southern%20drawl%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20wave%20to%20strangers%20as%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-im-moving-from-the-south-back-to-new-york-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrove%20down%20the%20street%20in%20Kentucky%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20New%20York%2C%20I%20loved%20being%20exposed%20to%20culture%20through%20museums%20and%20art%20shows.%20It%20felt%20like%20the%20world%20was%20at%20my%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204a22067-0bbf-490c-b407-f8a747e97401%5C%22%3EMy%20grandfather%20taught%20me%20about%20hard%20work%20and%20giving%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20four%20idols%20growing%20up%3A%20Mohammed%20Ali%2C%20basketball%20legend%20Julius%20Irving%2C%20business%20magnate%20Howard%20Hughes%2C%20and%20my%20grandfather.%20As%20I%20read%20about%20and%20watched%20these%20men%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleadership-lessons-jimmy-carter-legacy-president-death-mistakes-management-negotiation-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elearned%20about%20leadership%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandfather%2C%20whom%20I'm%20named%20for%2C%20knew%20about%20hard%20work.%20When%20he%20was%2014%2C%20he%20started%20sweeping%20floors%20in%20a%20tobacco%20plant.%20He%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20until%20he%20became%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Tobacco%20Association%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20hate%20me%20for%20it%2C%20although%20big%20tobacco%20had%20its%20problems%2C%20my%20grandfather%20was%20a%20great%20man%20who%20was%20always%20intent%20on%20making%20people's%20lives%20better.%20He%20would%20pay%20for%20the%20college%20education%20of%20people%20who%20worked%20on%20our%20family%20farm.%20From%20him%2C%20I%20learned%20about%20working%20hard%20and%20giving%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222644%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ward%20Simmons%20and%20his%20father%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68625fb73d5881a51c1c56b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWard%20Simmons%20with%20his%20father.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ward%20Simmons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%2C%20a%20banker%2C%20taught%20me%20to%20always%20do%20things%20the%20right%20way.%20If%20I%20missed%20one%20weed%20in%20the%20garden%2C%20he'd%20have%20me%20out%20there%2C%20making%20my%20wrong%20right%20until%20the%20job%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273197989-e3d2-4368-bee0-c27a12f177b8%5C%22%3EWorking%20here%20has%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20power%20of%20writing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20lucky%20to%20apply%20the%20values%20my%20family%20gave%20me%20to%20the%20world.%20At%20Ralph%20Lauren%20I%20learned%20about%20beauty%3B%20in%20marketing%20at%20Hugo%20Boss%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20take%20that%20beauty%20and%20pair%20it%20with%20the%20magic%20of%20the%20brand%20in%20order%20to%20drive%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoleskine%20is%20d