0profitable%20software%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20JPMorgan%20said%20OpenAI%20faces%20some%20risk%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20AI%20models%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjohnny-ive-openai-chatgpt-distribution-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperform%20pretty%20similarly%20these%20days%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20bank%20views%20OpenAI's%20models%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20fragile%20moat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20conclusion%2C%20we%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20having%20the%20'best%20AI%20model'%20is%20a%20robust%20enough%20moat%20or%20differentiating%20factor%20as%20competitors%20will%20follow%20suit%20soon%20after%2C%26quot%3B%20JPMorgan%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20and%20JPMorgan%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-jpmorgan-vibe-spending-test-investors-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753088401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686ddada85e81483682d9e06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-jpmorgan-vibe-spending-test-investors-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Find%20out%20what%20JPMorgan%20has%20to%20say%20about%20OpenAI's%20prospects%20in%20its%20first-ever%20research%20note%20about%20a%20private%20firm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22crollet%40insider.com%20(Charles%20Rollet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-jpmorgan-vibe-spending-test-investors-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Embrace%20the%20chaos%3A%20A%20Morgan%20Stanley%20derivatives%20exec%20on%20life%20at%20the%20desk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224857%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iliana%20Bouzali%2C%20co-head%20of%20equity%20derivatives