Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20all%20eyes%20on%20this%20booming%20business%2C%20Business%20Insider%20set%20out%20to%20shine%20a%20spotlight%20on%20Wall%20Street's%20sales%20and%20trading%20business.%20What's%20life%20like%20at%20the%20desk%3F%20What%20does%20it%20take%20to%20thrive%20in%20this%20fast-paced%20job%3F%20And%20what%20should%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-intern-survival-guide-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eyoung%20people%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20aspiring%20to%20work%20in%20sell-side%20sales%20and%20trading%20know%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20answers%2C%20we%20turned%20to%20Iliana%20Bouzali%2C%20cohead%20of%20equity%20derivatives%20for%20Morgan%20Stanley.%20She%20started%20her%20career%20as%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-investment-banking-internship-wall-street-summer-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eintern%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%20in%202003.%20She%20was%20pursuing%20an%20architecture%20degree%20at%20Yale%2C%20but%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20trading%20floor%20and%20never%20looked%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20energy%20of%20a%20trading%20floor%20is%20like%20nothing%20else.%20It's%20not%20for%20everyone%2C%20but%20if%20you%20like%20it%2C%20you%20love%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20flat%20architecture%2C%20there's%20no%20hierarchy.%20If%20you%20have%20something%20useful%20to%20say%2C%20you%20say%20it.%20If%20there's%20a%20problem%20to%20solve%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20your%20title%20is%2C%20you%20solve%20the%20problem.%20And%20it%20can%20be%20very%20infectious%2C%20so%20I%20was%20hooked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20you're%20pitching%20clients%20on%20the%20products%20they%20need%20to%20grow%20and%20prot