%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBouzali%2C%20for%20example%2C%20admitted%20to%20feeling%20both%20excited%20and%20terrified%20during%20her%20first%20summer%20on%20the%20trading%20floor%2C%20and%20was%20worried%20she%20didn't%20know%20enough%20about%20finance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20not%20compare%20yourself%20to%20peers%20and%20start%20competing%20against%20a%20more%20honest%20metric%20%E2%80%94%20the%20version%20of%20yourself%20that%20plays%20it%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22403098e6-7874-409c-94e8-32cc7ca42ba8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearn%20to%20deal%20with%20%26quot%3Bopacity%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20Bouzali's%20earliest%20lessons%20was%20learning%20not%20to%20expect%20the%20structure%20and%20direction%20she%20was%20used%20to%20at%20university%2C%20where%20the%20path%20to%20success%20is%20clearly%20laid%20out%20in%20syllabi%20and%20measured%20via%20homework%20and%20tests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BA%20trading%20floor%20is%20particularly%20opaque%2C%20and%20that%20ambiguity%20is%20a%20feature%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20bug%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20that's%20confusing%2C%20it's%20meant%20to%20be%2C%20Bouzali%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20I%20try%20to%20convey%20to%20our%20interns%20early%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20not%20always%20be%20handed%20tasks%20or%20told%20exactly%20what%20to%20do%20and%20how%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpacity%20is%20not%20a%20signal%20to%20wait%2C%20but%20to%20move%2C%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20throw%20yourself%20into%20problems.%20You%20have%20to%20sniff%20out%20what%20matters%20and%20what%20doesn't%20matter.%20You%20have%20to%20pin%20point%20what%20people's%