%26quot%3BDon't%20obsess%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BJust%20focus%20on%20winning%20the%20next%206%20to%2012%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGetting%20things%20done%20versus%20chasing%20titles%20will%20naturally%20lead%20you%20to%20the%20next%20big%20thing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BPromotions%20don't%20follow%20ambition.%20They%20follow%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20Bouzali%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20better%20question%20than%20'How%20do%20I%20get%20ahead%3F'%20is%20'What%20are%20the%20hard%20things%20that%20need%20to%20get%20done%20that%20I%20could%20do%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d311b91-dbad-4733-9ca1-306fcafa3b1d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearn%20to%20slow%20down%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBouzali's%20job%20demands%20she%20stay%20up%20to%20speed%20on%20the%20news%20and%20market%20at%20all%20times%2C%20so%20she%20uses%20reading%20as%20a%20way%20to%20diversify%20her%20perspectives%20outside%20the%20here%20and%20now.%20From%20obscure%20medieval%20history%20to%20art%20criticism%20and%20strange%20fiction%2C%20she%20prefers%20to%20read%20things%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20beaten%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20try%20to%20avoid%20the%20super%20contemporary%20and%20super%20trendy%20because%20I%20really%20want%20to%20develop%20completely%20different%20mental%20threads%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bouzali%20of%20her%20book%20choices.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20very%20good%20for%20me%20to%20just%20step%20completely%20outside%20of%20what%20is%20trendy%20here%20and%20now%20and%20find%20older%2C%20slower%20modes%20of%20thought.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmorgan-stanley-iliana-bouzali-sales-trading-floor-derivatives-career-advice-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2