p%20fairytale%20%E2%80%94%20until%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwindsurf-google-cognition-acquisition-ai-coding-developer-data-ide-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeal%20fell%20through%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20setting%20off%20a%20whirlwind%20of%20last-minute%20negotiations%20that%20left%20employees%20grappling%20with%20uncertainty%2C%20and%20a%20company%20split%20in%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unusual%20dismantling%20of%20the%20company%20into%20separate%20parts%20of%20haves%20and%20have-nots%20has%20left%20a%20bitter%20taste%20for%20some%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20breaks%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20social%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amjad%20Masad%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECEO%20of%20Replit%2C%20a%20competitor%20to%20Windsurf.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20bad%20for%20startup%20employees.%20They're%20going%20to%20be%20less%20likely%20to%20join%20startups.%20What's%20the%20point%20of%20joining%20a%20startup%20and%20working%20your%20ass%20off%20if%20you%20might%20get%20screwed%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20that%20the%20kind%20of%20life-changing%20event%20early%20startup%20employees%20dream%20about%20happened%20at%20Windsurf%3A%20OpenAI%20announced%20it%20was%20buying%20the%20AI-powered%20coding%20startup%20for%20%243%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20read%20the%20news%2C%20Dave%20Pack%2C%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20startup%20founder%2C%20opened%20a%20group%20chat%20and%20congratulated%20his%20friend%20who%20works%20at%20Windsurf%2C%20whom%20he%20declined%20to%20name.%20He%20joked%20that%20with%20his%20friend's%20sudden%20change%20in%20net%20worth%2C%20he%20could%20afford%20to%20foot%20the%20bill%20for%20their%20next%20guys'%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20really%20excited%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Pack%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20pretty%20senior%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20like%20he%20had%20a%20small%20chunk%20of%20equity.%20When%20you%20join%20a%20comp