%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20systems%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20smooth%20operations%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20water-softening%20unit%20to%20avoid%20mineral%20buildup%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20pressure%20reducer%20to%20keep%20the%20steam%20flow%20consistent%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnd%20a%20diesel%20backup%20system%20(only%20used%20during%20the%20monsoon)%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20during%20cloudy%20days%20and%20rain%2C%20the%20kitchen%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stop.%20That%20backup%20diesel%20setup%20keeps%20meals%20flowing%2C%20making%20it%20reliable%20year-round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%2020%2C000%20to%2050%2C000%20meals%20a%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20system%20was%20first%20fully%20commissioned%20in%201998%2C%20it%20was%20designed%20to%20cook%2020%2C000%20meals%20a%20day.%20But%20it%20quickly%20outperformed%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20expanding%20the%20infrastructure%2C%20improving%20efficiency%2C%20and%20adding%20more%20modules%2C%20the%20kitchen%20now%20serves%20up%20to%2050%2C000%20people%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mix%20of%20residents%2C%20volunteers%2C%20guests%2C%20and%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20equivalent%20of%20feeding%20an%20entire%20stadium%20every%20single%20day%20with%20sunlight!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20this%20solar%20kitchen%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20in%201992%20as%20a%20small%20experiment%20is%20now%20an%20international%20model%20for%20clean%2C%20large-scale%20cooking.%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%20backed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20New%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352853%2Fgadge-meenakshi-mukhra-ecovillage-telangana-solar-power-plantation-drives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERenewable%20Energy%3C%2F